    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761080/extras/7a8be64d771a03ff551c64f58e4b3f25.poster.avif?t=1746541411\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761080/extras/7a8be64d771a03ff551c64f58e4b3f25.webm?t=1746541411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761080/extras/7a8be64d771a03ff551c64f58e4b3f25.mp4?t=1746541411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Quest of Wizard是一款设定在奇幻世界中的经典动作平台游戏。穿越充满危险陷阱和困难敌人的关卡，与Boss战斗，寻找装满金币的宝箱和秘密，学习并升级法术。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761080/extras/8021dea140360ba3261ec537aa805e1e.poster.avif?t=1746541411\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761080/extras/8021dea140360ba3261ec537aa805e1e.webm?t=1746541411\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761080/extras/8021dea140360ba3261ec537aa805e1e.mp4?t=1746541411\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 魔法战斗系统以及无敌冲刺。<br></li><li> 驾驭四大元素主法术，并以辅助法术，被动技能和属性升级进一步强化角色。<br></li><li> 5大关卡，每大关中有4个小关和1个Boss。<br></li><li> 20种不同敌人，各有危险之处。<br></li><li> 在平台间腾挪转移。<br></li><li> 尖刺，落石，枪炮，毒气，强风等致命陷阱。<br></li><li> Xbox 360/PS4手柄支持。<br></li><li> 可自选难度。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761080/extras/3c1f18f06aa3dee010499fe21adf38c9.poster.avif?t=1746541411\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1761080